text: do you want to know what some of my
favorite dances are I remember learning
a Chinese ribbon dance it was really
beautiful moving the long red ribbons
and waves and circles I also liked the
challenge of learning tinikling which is
a Filipino dance with long bamboo sticks
basically if you don't pick up your feet
at the right time you're going to get
them caught in between two fast-moving
poles but my favorite dance to learn was
the Hawaiian hula I think it's wonderful
to combine music song and dance to tell
a story
